# Svobodny, Republic of Adygea

}}
Svobodny () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Khatukayskoye Rural Settlement of Krasnogvardeysky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 8 as of 2018. There are 5 streets.
Geography
Svobodny is located 6 km north of Krasnogvardeyskoye (the district's administrative centre) by road. Vodny is the nearest rural locality.
